criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients ≥18 years;

          -  patients suffering an acute kidney injury (defined by Acute kidney injury network
             (AKIN) score ≥1)during ICU stay.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients <18 years;

          -  pregnant woman;

          -  End stage renal disease (ESRD)prior to ICU admission;

          -  Refusal to participate in the study.
